Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:31.04,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.15}盤算著壞事的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:45.80,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.15}{\c&H00FFFFFF}離彆氣息藏於口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:52.98,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.15}回憶是一幅黑白畫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.14,0:22:58.40,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.15}{\c&H00FFFFFF}請將其賦予色彩吧
